
files
  - .babelrc -> babel configuration file
  - .eslintignore -> eslint ignore rules
  - .eslintrc -> eslint configuration file
  - nodemon.js -> nodemont configuration file
  - webpack.config.babel.js -> for dev server runtime compile in index.js (server:watch)
  - webpack.config.server.js -> for prod server build (server:build)
  - index.js -> server entry point

scripts
  - server:watch -> starts nodemon (see nodemon.json)
  - server:build -> build server to dist
  - server:start -> starts production server

dependencies:
  - nodemon -> restart node on failure and watches for changes (see nodemon.js)
  - cross-env -> standard environment variables between OS
  - express
  - morgan -> express midleware for logs
  - body-parser -> express midleware for body parsing
  - react
  - react-dom


devDependencies
  - webpack               -> pack server for production, loaders
  - webpack-dev-middleware -> middleware to create dev server
  - webpack-hot-middleware -> meddleware hot reloading of modules dev server
  - react-hot-loader      -> Tweak React components in real time(<AppContainer>)
  - babel-core
  - babel-loader
  - babel-cli             -> compile server es6
  - babel-preset-es2015   -> preset for babel ?
  - babel-react           -> preset react jsx
  - babel-stage-0         -> next generation js ?
  - babel-plugin-webplack-loaders -> link babel to webpack

  - eslint                -> lint js code (see .eslintrc.json/.eslintignore)
  - eslint-config-airbnb
  - eslint-plugin-import
  - eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y

  - style-loader
  - css-loader
